{"tid":1888083,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"doinb 個老婆真係cls 睇呢段採訪睇到眼濕濕","createTime":"2020-02-20T03:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T06:07:49.000Z","uid":136738,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"44f7122dada7bf60fa31af6339552007c17a9299","tid":1888083,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G9elJgE8Amg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG9elJgE8Amg&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=f3768b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G9elJgE8Amg</a><br />\n<br />\n3:38開始<br />\n<br />\ndoinb諗過話退役<br />\n係佢老婆鼓勵佢打多一年先繼續打落去<br />\n<br />\ndoinb老婆每場比賽都會去睇<br />\n仲要基本上係佢地啦啦隊隊長<br />\nd lpl比賽直播仲會聽到佢大叫到d旁述話：<br />\n啊 doinb老婆喺到為佢地打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時會同老公一齊開台 <br />\n見到老公撩其他女主播會嬲<br />\n<br />\n比著香港女仔<br />\n由識條友第一日一定叫佢退役退到佢攞世界冠軍為止<br />\n每日就會鼓勵佢退役 叫佢搵份正正經經嘅工<br />\n點同老豆老母交代男朋友係電競師啊<br />\n每日催幾時結婚 幾時買樓<br />\n出糧就lur老公買名牌 香水 化妝品<br />\n<br />\n其實淨係陪老公追夢呢個過程已經好浪漫<br />\n但係香港人淨係就會睇結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e06ad96ae892293281789fcab516a9e74bc4715","tid":1888083,"uid":59192,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"起底&gt;負評&gt;上一頁"},{"pid":"becff21442b07be0a3a863e627f146b313872876","tid":1888083,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6e06ad96ae892293281789fcab516a9e74bc4715","tid":1888083,"uid":59192,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"起底&gt;負評&gt;上一頁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"6d89c594e18a038d95a84e59215cd7c217328f34","tid":1888083,"uid":207325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"香港太瘋狂<br />\n港女覺得自己係公主"},{"pid":"281d9a53bcb5edf0d517f23b30554bc48808c013","tid":1888083,"uid":5971,"like":